largest stablecoins, cryptocurrencies pegged to the dollar.=C2=A0=C2=A0</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Maple Finance is among a host of crypto firms =
seizing on the higher yields and relative safety offered by U.S. government=
