=E2=80=9D and receive tokens that represent their ownership in exchange. Th=
e pool then issues a loan to an entity managed by crypto hedge fund Room40 =
Capital, which will invest customer deposits in one-month Treasury bills.</=
p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Is this product better than a money market fun=
